{"tid":2099684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［推上熱門] 流亡資訊平台「避風驛」將為有需要人士提供免費諮詢","createTime":"2020-07-08T11:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T12:28:00.000Z","uid":321421,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9434652ca39e9c33bd854a3f635e217a86a06db0","tid":2099684,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"Haven Assistance Joint Statement <br />\n避風驛聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\nWe believe that the National Security Law promulgated by Beijing in Hong Kong represses dissent and results in the death of the &quot;One Country, Two Systems&quot; framework. <br />\n我們相信北京在香港頒布的《國家安全法》壓制了異議，並導致了「一國兩制」框架的消亡。<br />\n<br />\nAs pro-democracy activists in exile, our first duty is to protect the citizens of Hong Kong. Therefore, we have set up an information-sharing platform, Haven Assistance, for people who may need help to access reliable information. <br />\n作為流亡的民主運動人士，我們的首要職責是保護香港市民。因此我們為可能需要幫助的人們提供共享資訊的平台，也就是「避風驛」。<br />\n<br />\nThis platform will act as a resource for people to obtain information about asylum policies in the United States, Taiwan, the United Kingdom, Germany, and other countries. A team of professionals also stand ready to provide free legal advice in the UK for those who need it. <br />\n該平台將提供美國、台灣、英國、德國和其他國家庇護政策訊息資源。目前我們有一支專業團隊，為身處英國有需要的人提供免費的法律諮詢服務。<br />\n<br />\nWe are grateful for the courage shown by the UK in setting up a lifeboat scheme for Hongkongers, however, we currently await more details of the plan as well as those being considered by other democratic allies such as Canada, Australia, and the US. <br />\n我們感謝英國為香港人打造救生艇計劃表現出的勇氣，但是我們目前仍在與其他民主陣營盟友跟進該計劃的更多細節，例如加拿大、澳洲和美國正在考慮施行的細節。<br />\n<br />\nWe also urge the international community to stand with people staying in Hong Kong by providing a safety net and empowering them to continue the pro-democracy cause without hindrance.<br />\n我們亦敦促國際社會與留在香港的人們站在一起，提供安全網，並賦權予他們在沒有阻礙的情況下，繼續推進民主事業。<br />\n<br />\nHaven Assistance Joint Organizer <br />\n避風驛聯合發起人<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Leung KP (US) 梁繼平 &bull; 美國<br />\n&bull; Ray Wong (Germany) 黃台仰 &bull; 德國<br />\n&bull; Simon Cheng (UK) 鄭文傑 &bull; 英國<br />\n&bull; Lam Wing Kee (Taiwan) 林榮基 &bull; 台灣<br />\n<br />\n* If any overseas Hong Kong organization is willing to be a part of this collaborative network, please reach out to the organizers. <br />\n如果有任何海外香港組織願意加入合作，歡迎與發起人聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoNCDeM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoNCDeM.jpg&h=6083a8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HavenAssistance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHavenAssistance%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=c7013b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HavenAssistance/</a>"},{"pid":"40d5cbc6b251639d613816dfc9519627c1445525","tid":2099684,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"推俾有需要嘅手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cece2a79fdcbca5ec42a52c423e0742fe0dbcaf2","tid":2099684,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db8a09923bc5fbd83b34d053e1183e35eac5c21","tid":2099684,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cece2a79fdcbca5ec42a52c423e0742fe0dbcaf2","tid":2099684,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2843558550d01277d015712c25f7698526f3690","tid":2099684,"uid":